form surat tugas :
-Tanggal Pengajuan (date) (has hidden hour:minutes timestamp)
-Tanggal Kegiatan dimulai (date)
-Tanggal Kegiatan berakhir (date)
-Nama Kegiatan (string)
-Jenis Kegiatan (online/offline dropdown)
-PIC (dropdown user role PIC)
-Nama Pendamping (string) (optional)
-Fee Pendamping (money in rupiah) (optional)
-Instruktor (dynamic add):
-Nama Instruktor (string)
-Fee Instruktor (money in rupiah)
-Total fee (automatic count all money in form)

form nomor surat :
make the nomor surat form into this :
-Tanggal pengajuan (date)
-Pilihan Bendera(dropdown list of bendera : placeholder data is SPP, MBS, EPU, KIM, PrimaOne)
-Tujuan Surat (string)
-Nama Klien (string)
-Catatan (long string)

form invoice :
-Tanggal Pengajuan (date)
-Tanggal Invoice (date)
-Kegiatan (string)
-Tagihan invoice ()
-PPN (dropdown include,exclude,tanpa ppn)
change the rincian item to Rincian Invoice OPE
-Total invoice (tagihan invoice + 11% of tagihan invoice if include ppn + total rincian)
-Upload Bukti Confirmation Letter (pdf format upload)
